title: Lovers
info:
ZX Spectrum AY soundchip track, written with Vortex Tracker II Version 1.2 improved RC 2 for Chaos Constructions 2013 demoparty.

The image is taken from [url=http://pouet.net/prod.php?which=54378]"A true story from the life of a lonely cell"[/url], a ZX Spectrum intro by [group]246[/group] and [group]554[/group].
